  "title": "Food Production Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>We are from central kitchen in food manufacturing sector located in Singapore, fostering a positive work environment—\"Work Hard, Play Hard!\" We're looking for passionate supervisory professionals to join our family!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Position:</strong> Production Supervisor</p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> From $3,000 onwards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise production workers to ensure smooth and efficient operations.</li>\n  <li>Implement production schedules and assign tasks to meet production targets.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with food safety and workplace safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>Train, coach, and evaluate production staff to improve performance and efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Monitor equipment functionality and coordinate maintenance when necessary.</li>\n  <li>Identify and resolve production issues in a timely manner.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate production records and generate reports for management.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with quality control teams to ensure product quality meets standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong leadership and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in shifts and adapt to changing production demands.</li>\n  <li>Experience in troubleshooting production-related issues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ 20 days of paid leave</p>\n<p>✔ Medical benefits &amp; insurance coverage</p>\n<p>✔ Various allowances &amp; incentives (Meal allowances, Revenue Incentives, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Various bonuses (AWS, performance, attendance)</p>\n<p>✔ Various rewards (Best Employee Award, Long services award, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Strong career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>✔ Revenue incentives</p>\n<p>✔ Sponsored courses for career growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you’re the right fit for our team, send your application here! We look forward to your application!</strong></p>",
